{"tid":1416314,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[鄰里關係] 如果你知道鄰居係警察","createTime":"2019-08-05T14:52:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T15:04:19.000Z","uid":57269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"61c8c3e3798391e43d8bb7049b66f1462d2d0de4","tid":1416314,"uid":57269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:52:56.000Z","msg":"紀律部隊宿舍嘅居民，受到警察家庭嘅影響，連累自己生活受影響，你會用咩眼光望佢家人小朋友。我好擔心警察哥哥一家瞓唔安、坐唔落、每晚有人禁鐘問候。千萬不要公布警察嘅住址去標簽無辜嘅小朋友。"},{"pid":"48ffa989ec4c9012627129e8356888ad83a15965","tid":1416314,"uid":57269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:03:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c5746b878350538cfcb3515005a8dda75e8021b","tid":1416314,"uid":57269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:04:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a417dee9d5fb991bf004a300e4f014a02d646ad3","tid":1416314,"uid":57269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:04:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}